Hug your Baby!! 🤰🏼 “Abrazo del bebé” 🐣 Este ejercicio de respiración profunda es la base de todos mis ejercicios/workouts prenatales 🤸🏼‍♀️. Consiste en activar el transverso del abdomen, el core desde suelo pélvico, espalda y diafragma a través de la respiración. 

Lo puedes realizar en varias posiciones, de pie, de rodillas, sentada etc. 🤓

Conjuntito de @lenoremoves 🫶🏻 uni talla, se adapta a todos los cuerpos. Mi salvación!!

📷 @margentamedia

From that first click at age 8, photography became a source of joy.  They sparked a passion that has grown with me, shaping my dreams and leading me to where I am today: A professional photographer & content creator who cherishes the joy of moments that last a lifetime.

The heart of my journey lies in preserving the raw emotions, genuine connections, and the unspoken stories that unfold in every snapshot. What truly fulfills me is the happiness I can bring to those in front of my lens.

I feel privileged to have a career that embodies my lifestyle…a constant celebration of creativity, connection, and the pursuit of capturing life's most meaningful moments. ✨
